data.description: Beautiful well-maintained and cared for Silvercrest manufactured home located on a quiet lot in Via Verde, one of the most desirable land-owned 55+ parks in the county. It is a 2 br 2 ba 1536 sq ft home with updated baths and large closets. This home is an open design style with high ceilings and a combined living room and dining room. Lots of closets for storage, and carport with a storage shed and motion sensor lights. It is in a very unique park in that you can walk your dog right there in the park - one of the few parks where you can walk your dog. Solar system included. It is strategically located within close proximity of freeway access, grocery stores, gas station, and restaurants.  Could this be your “forever home?”  Come and visit to see if this home is just what you've been searching for! This will make a wonderful home for someone who is down-sizing!!
